#. …おう、全員ここに集まったのか？
msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Not long after I got to the dining hall, the others\n"
"began to trickle in.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. あのね、いい事教えてあげよっか。
#. モノクマが言うにはね…
msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>And after a few minutes...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 全員でこのジェットコースターに乗ると、
#. ご褒美が貰えるらしいんだよね。
msgctxt "0003"
msgid "So, is this everyone?"
msgstr ""

#. オ、オレは乗んねーからな！
msgctxt "0004"
msgid "Okay, let's discuss what we all discovered."
msgstr ""

#. 言わなかったっけ？
#. オレは乗り物酔いがヒデーんだよ！
msgctxt "0005"
msgid "Yeah, good idea..."
msgstr ""

#. ガオー！　いらっしゃーい！
msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"I found a couple rooms on the 4th floor, but they were\n"
"locked! The <CLT 3>data center<CLT> and the <CLT 3>headmaster's room<CLT>!"
msgstr ""

#. 当園の目玉アトラクションである、
#. <CLT 03>『ウルトラデリシャスグレートコースター』<CLT>でーす！
msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"The headmaster's room!? That sounds like exactly the\n"
"kinda place we'd find some clues!"
msgstr ""

#. で、これに乗るとご褒美が貰えるってのは、
#. ホントなんか？
msgctxt "0008"
msgid "If we can somehow unlock the door and get inside..."
msgstr ""

#. もっちろんでーす！
msgctxt "0009"
msgid "Who cares about a stupid lock!"
msgstr ""

#. ご褒美って…なんだよ？
msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"It should be no problem for the world's strongest\n"
"missing link to knock down one measly door!"
msgstr ""

#. ヤですよぉ！
#. それは乗ってからのお楽しみじゃないですか！
msgctxt "0011"
msgid "...What was that?"
msgstr ""

#. なァ…全員で乗らねーとダメなのかよ…？
msgctxt "0012"
msgid "Uwah!"
msgstr ""

#. そう言ってんじゃん。その耳はイラストかい？
msgctxt "0013"
msgid "No, please. Continue."
msgstr ""

#. イヤだッ！　オレはイヤだぞッ！！
msgctxt "0014"
msgid ""
"Did you say I've got the nicest butt on the block? The\n"
"curviest hips in town? Is that what you said!?"
msgstr ""

#. まぁまぁ、大丈夫だって！
#. 絶叫マシーンとか楽しいぜ！
msgctxt "0015"
msgid "Hell no I didn't!"
msgstr ""

#. 言うよな！　好きなヤツはそう言うよな！
#. でも全然楽しくねーって知ってんだぞ！
msgctxt "0016"
msgid ""
"Then what DID you say? Cuz I KNOW you weren't talking\n"
"about tearing down the door to the headmaster's room."
msgstr ""

#. けどよ…そのご褒美ってのが、
#. "船の部品"って可能性もあるんじゃねーか？
msgctxt "0017"
msgid "Ng—!"
msgstr ""

#. そ、それは…そうかもしんねーけどよォ…
msgctxt "0018"
msgid ""
"Knocking down your headmaster's door? What kind of war\n"
"on education are you trying to start here!?"
msgstr ""

#. ところで…この乗り物はどこに向かうのですか？
msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"That's MY room, ya know? It is *now*, anyway... And\n"
"you're thinking of busting it down?"
msgstr ""

#. どこにも向かわないよ。
#. グルッと回って戻って来るだけだもん。
msgctxt "0020"
msgid ""
"You seriously don't wanna piss me off. You have any\n"
"idea how much bacteria lives on a single bear claw?"
msgstr ""

#. それには…どのような意味があるのでしょうか。
msgctxt "0021"
msgid "N-No, I was just kiddin'! Please don't get mad!"
msgstr ""

#. …貴様は遊園地に行った事がないのか？
msgctxt "0022"
msgid "I'm not mad! >_<"
msgstr ""

#. 恥ずかしながら、
#. わたくしの国にはありませんでしたので。
msgctxt "0023"
msgid "You're totally mad! ;_;"
msgstr ""

#. そうか…かく言う俺様も幼少の頃に
#. １度だけ行っただけだ…
msgctxt "0024"
msgid ""
"I was hoping I wouldn't have to add a rule for this,\n"
"but if you're gonna go around having those thoughts..."
msgstr ""

#. 悪鬼羅刹で埋め尽くされた地獄の遊園地だがな！
msgctxt "0025"
msgid ""
"I have no choice but to <CLT 3>add to the school\n"
"regulations<CLT>!"
msgstr ""

#. えっ！？　地獄にも遊園地がっ！？
msgctxt "0026"
msgid "Seriously...?"
msgstr ""

#. それは初耳でした！
#. 是非、今度ご一緒させてください！
msgctxt "0027"
msgid ""
"<CLT 3>Breaking down a locked door is prohibited<CLT>! There,\n"
"that's a rule now, ya jerks!"
msgstr ""

#. ダメですって、ソニアさんッ！
#. そいつには虚言癖があるんですからッ！
msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>The new rule has been added to the <CLT><CLT 3>Regulations<CLT><CLT 23> menu.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 入場料は処女の血だ！
#. 貴様の血を生贄にしてくれよう！
msgctxt "0029"
msgid "I-Is he gone...?"
msgstr ""

#. それは…困りましたね…
#. わたくしの血では入場料にならなそうです。
msgctxt "0030"
msgid ""
"Whew... Man, I was scared for my life! I was sure he\n"
"was gonna kill me, for serious!"
msgstr ""

#. えッ？　という事は…ソニアさん！？
msgctxt "0031"
msgid ""
"But if he would go out of his way to make up a rule\n"
"like that..."
msgstr ""

#. ねぇ、みんな…
#. こんな所で時間を潰してても仕方がないし…
msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"...there's no doubt that <CLT 3>something important<CLT> must be\n"
"hidden in the headmaster's room."
msgstr ""

#. とりあえず乗ってみない？
msgctxt "0033"
msgid "But...now that it's a rule, there's nothing we can do."
msgstr ""

#. ちょ、ちょっと待て！
#. どうして、とりあえずで乗るんだよ！
msgctxt "0034"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. …弐大クン、お願いしてもいいかな？
msgctxt "0035"
msgid ""
"So <CLT 3>breaking into a locked room<CLT> is against the rules\n"
"now..."
msgstr ""

#. 任せんかあああああああああいっ！！
msgctxt "0036"
msgid ""
"If he would go out of his way to make up a rule like\n"
"that..."
msgstr ""

#. や、やめろッ！
#. やめて…お願い、放してッ！！
msgctxt "0037"
msgid ""
"...there's no doubt that <CLT 3>something important<CLT> must be\n"
"hidden in the headmaster's room."
msgstr ""

#. 放してくれえええええええッ！！
msgctxt "0038"
msgid "But...now that it's a rule, there's nothing we can do."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>必死の抵抗も虚しく、
#. 左右田はジェットコースターに押し込まれ…<CLT>
msgctxt "0039"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. ウルトラデリシャスグレートコースター！
#. それでは出発進行でーす！！
msgctxt "0040"
msgid ""
"There was a big shelf in the <CLT 3>chem lab<CLT> on the 4th\n"
"floor, and it had all kinds of chemicals and stuff."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>そんなモノクマの掛け声と共に、
#. ジェットコースターはマックススピードで発進した！<CLT>
msgctxt "0041"
msgid ""
"And there was an all-star cast of nutrient additives\n"
"and supplements!"
msgstr ""

#. ひゃっほーーーーーーーい！！
msgctxt "0042"
msgid ""
"You should at least go take a peek. I highly recommend\n"
"it!"
msgstr ""

#. アーッ、アーーーッ！！
msgctxt "0043"
msgid ""
"I think you and Ogre are probably the only ones\n"
"interested in stuff like that..."
msgstr ""

#. 死ぬッ…死ぬうううううううッ！！
msgctxt "0044"
msgid "Oh, but...it's not all good stuff, though."
msgstr ""

#. ぐっ…凄まじい重力じゃあのぉ！
#. 体中のネジが吹き飛ぶようじゃぞぉおおおお！
msgctxt "0045"
msgid ""
"There was medicine and health stuff, but on top of\n"
"that..."
msgstr ""

#. 鎮まれッ…俺様の心臓よッ！
msgctxt "0046"
msgid "There was also, um...a bunch of different <CLT 3>poisons<CLT>."
msgstr ""

#. で、でもっ！　楽しいですっ！
msgctxt "0047"
msgid "P-Poison!?"
msgstr ""

#. し…し…死ぬぅ……
#. 死なせて……くれぇ…………
msgctxt "0048"
msgid ""
"They were all labeled clearly, though. So it would be\n"
"hard to grab one by mistake..."
msgstr ""

#. はーい、到着でーす！
#. どう？　面白かったでしょ？
msgctxt "0049"
msgid ""
"Still, we'd better make sure we're careful around\n"
"there."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>や、やっと終わったか…
#. さすがにちょっと…キツかったな…<CLT>
msgctxt "0050"
msgid ""
"And...we probably shouldn't tell Byakuya or Toko about\n"
"the poison, right?"
msgstr ""

#. なぁなぁ！　もっかい乗ろうぜ！
msgctxt "0051"
msgid "What do you mean...?"
msgstr ""

#. いいですね、そうしましょう！
msgctxt "0052"
msgid ""
"Well, <CLT 3>just in case<CLT>... You know what I'm trying to\n"
"say."
msgstr ""

#. イヤだッ！　ぜってーにイヤだああああッ！！
msgctxt "0053"
msgid "J-Just in case... Yeah, I think you're right."
msgstr ""

#. …ねぇ、それよりご褒美は？
msgctxt "0054"
msgid ""
"It's Byakuya. It won't be long before he's discovered\n"
"it for himself."
msgstr ""

#. あぁ、そうだったね！
#. はーい、ご褒美はこのファイルでーす！！
msgctxt "0055"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>But to put something as dangerous as poison right out\n"
"in the open...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. …え！？
msgctxt "0056"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>That's absolutely the work of the mastermind.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>こ、このマークって…！<CLT>
msgctxt "0057"
msgid ""
"There was a big shelf in the <CLT 3>chem lab<CLT> on the 4th\n"
"floor, and it had all kinds of chemicals and stuff."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>あの遺跡の扉にあったのと…同じマークだ！<CLT>
msgctxt "0058"
msgid ""
"And there was an all-star cast of nutrient additives\n"
"and supplements!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>だとすると、このファイルって…<CLT>
msgctxt "0059"
msgid ""
"But there was also, um...a bunch of different\n"
"<CLT 3>poisons<CLT>."
msgstr ""

#. …未来機関のファイルって事か！
#. これを見れば未来機関の正体がわかるのか！？
msgctxt "0060"
msgid ""
"They were all labeled clearly, though. So it would be\n"
"hard to grab one by mistake..."
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0061"
msgid ""
"Still, we'd better make sure we're careful around\n"
"there."
msgstr ""

#. 中を…確認させて貰っていいかな？
msgctxt "0062"
msgid ""
"And...we probably shouldn't tell Byakuya or Toko about\n"
"the poison, right?"
msgstr ""

#. はーい、お好きにどうぞ！
msgctxt "0063"
msgid "You're right... <CLT 3>Just in case<CLT>..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>俺達はファイルを受け取った狛枝のもとに、
#. 集まると…<CLT>
msgctxt "0064"
msgid ""
"It's Byakuya. It won't be long before he's discovered\n"
"it for himself."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>慎重な手付きでめくられていくファイルに、
#. じっと見入った。<CLT>
msgctxt "0065"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>To put something as dangerous as poison right out in\n"
"the open...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 06><CLT><CLT 03>"コロシアイ学園生活"<CLT><CLT 06>の舞台となったのは、
#. 皮肉にも希望ヶ峰学園だった。<CLT>
msgctxt "0066"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>That's absolutely the work of the mastermind.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 06>その計画の首謀者は…そこに学園の生徒達を閉じ込め、
#. 殺し合いを強要したのだ。<CLT>
msgctxt "0067"
msgid ""
"<CLT 3>Metal sheets<CLT> had been attached to all the windows on\n"
"the 4th floor. None of them budged an inch..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 06>極限状態に追い込まれた生徒達は、
#. やがて互いに疑心暗鬼を繰り返すようになり…<CLT>
msgctxt "0068"
msgid "Just like everywhere else..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 06>そして…殺し合いが始まった。<CLT>
msgctxt "0069"
msgid ""
"Escape from the 4th floor seems unlikely. That was to\n"
"be expected, though."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 06>その生徒達による殺し合いは、
#. 数日間にも及んだが…<CLT>
msgctxt "0070"
msgid "Um...Kyoko?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 06>ある時、唐突にその幕を下ろす事となる。<CLT>
msgctxt "0071"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. <CLT 06>団結した生徒達の反撃によって敗れた首謀者は、
#. そこで自らの命を絶ったのだ。<CLT>
msgctxt "0072"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>She's ignoring me...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 06>こうして生き残った<CLT><CLT 03>"６名の生徒達"<CLT><CLT 06>は、
#. 学園からの脱出に成功したのだが…<CLT>
msgctxt "0073"
msgid "Hey, Makoto..."
msgstr ""

#. ねぇ、この左側にある写真ってさ…
msgctxt "0074"
msgid "Does Kyoko seem upset to you?"
msgstr ""

#. その<CLT 03>"生き残りの６人"<CLT>の写真なのかな？
msgctxt "0075"
msgid "She is, isn't she!? She's totally mad!"
msgstr ""

#. だったら…これってどういう事なのかな？
msgctxt "0076"
msgid "Y-Yeah, it looks like it..."
msgstr ""

#. どうして…ここに<CLT 03>"彼"<CLT>がいるのかな？
msgctxt "0077"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. <CLT 04>と、狛枝が指差した先には…<CLT>
msgctxt "0078"
msgid ""
"I bet it's your fault, isn't it? You must've done\n"
"something to her."
msgstr ""

#. えっ！？
msgctxt "0079"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Agh...this is bad...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>別人のように痩せてはいたけど…
#. それは俺達の知る<CLT><CLT 03>"あいつ"<CLT><CLT 04>とそっくりだった。<CLT>
msgctxt "0080"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I can't leave now. I have to hear what everyone has to\n"
"say.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>超高校級の御曹司…十神白夜…<CLT>
msgctxt "0081"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>There's no point in leaving now. I have to hear what\n"
"everyone has to say.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>この島で最初の犠牲者になったあいつと、
#. そっくりだった。<CLT>
msgctxt "0082"
msgid "So...has everyone said what they need to say?"
msgstr ""

#. こ、これは確かに…十神のようだが…
msgctxt "0083"
msgid "I think so..."
msgstr ""

#. だが…なぜじゃあ！
#. なぜ、ここに十神が写っとるんじゃあっ！？
msgctxt "0084"
msgid ""
"But it looks like nobody found any clues at all, let\n"
"alone a way out of here."
msgstr ""

#. こ、これって…一体どういう事なの？
msgctxt "0085"
msgid ""
"I haven't been this depressed since my house burned to\n"
"the ground! Someone, do something to cheer me up!"
msgstr ""

#. つーか…この<CLT 03>"コロシアイ学園生活"<CLT>ってのは、
#. なんなんだよ！？
msgctxt "0086"
msgid "Um...can I say something?"
msgstr ""

#. ボクらが巻き込まれた<CLT 03>"コロシアイ"<CLT>と似たような事が、
#. 以前にも行われていたみたいだね…
msgctxt "0087"
msgid "It's cuz my dad was smoking in bed!"
msgstr ""

#. それも…"希望ヶ峰学園"の中でね。
msgctxt "0088"
msgid "That's...no... I have something I'd like to report."
msgstr ""

#. 待てや…こんな狂気じみた殺し合いが、
#. あの希望ヶ峰学園の中で起きてたってのか？
msgctxt "0089"
msgid "So...you guys all remember, right?"
msgstr ""

#. そんな訳ねーだろ！
#. センコー共や警察が放っておかねーぞ！
msgctxt "0090"
msgid ""
"You remember when I found that <CLT 3>picture<CLT> up on the 3rd\n"
"floor the other day?"
msgstr ""

#. だが…それを主導したのもまた、
#. <CLT 03>"世界の破壊者"<CLT>たる未来機関なのだとしたら？
msgctxt "0091"
msgid ""
"You mean the one that showed Mondo, Chihiro, and Leon\n"
"all together, right?"
msgstr ""

#. その組織が希望ヶ峰学園を
#. 制圧しちまったってのかぁ！？
msgctxt "0092"
msgid "Yeah, I remember. What about it?"
msgstr ""

#. あ、ある訳ねーだろ！　バカバカしい！！
msgctxt "0093"
msgid ""
"Well, I found another one. Another picture, almost\n"
"just like that one."
msgstr ""

#. 実際の参加者である十神クンが生きてれば、
#. 詳しい話を聞けたのに…
msgctxt "0094"
msgid "Another one...?"
msgstr ""

#. …残念だよ。
msgctxt "0095"
msgid ""
"But this time, the picture was of Celeste, Hifumi, and\n"
"Sayaka."
msgstr ""

#. ですが…わたくし達は記憶を失っているのですよね？
#. それは十神さんも同じだったはずです。
msgctxt "0096"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

#. それに…そんな過去があったなんて、
#. 十神さんは一言も言っていませんでしたし…
msgctxt "0097"
msgid "And they were all smiling..."
msgstr ""

#. …その前に殺されただけなのかもしれんがな。
msgctxt "0098"
msgid ""
"And the classroom in the picture didn't have any metal\n"
"covering the windows."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>言うヒマがないまま、
#. 最初の犠牲者になったって事か…？<CLT>
msgctxt "0099"
msgid ""
"So the picture of Mondo, Chihiro, and Leon wasn't the\n"
"only one..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>あ、もしかして…
#. 十神があの時言おうとしてたのって…<CLT>
msgctxt "0100"
msgid ""
"Now you found one that had Celeste, Hifumi, and\n"
"Sakaya?"
msgstr ""

#. 俺には人に語れないような過去がある…
#. 疑い深くなってるのはきっとそのせいだ。
msgctxt "0101"
msgid "But...how can that...?"
msgstr ""

#. 他人を疑い続け…そして疑われ続ける…
#. 俺はかつてそんな生き地獄のような生活を送った…
msgctxt "0102"
msgid "Monokuma must have faked it!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>あれは…この<CLT><CLT 03>"コロシアイ学園生活"<CLT><CLT 04>の事を
#. 指してたって事か…？<CLT>
msgctxt "0103"
msgid "But...if the picture *is* real..."
msgstr ""

#. とにかく…十神クンがいない以上は、
#. 仕方ないからモノクマに聞く事にするけどさ…
msgctxt "0104"
msgid "...then everyone who was in it..."
msgstr ""

#. 希望ヶ峰学園で起きた<CLT 03>"コロシアイ学園生活"<CLT>は、
#. この島で起きてる事とどう関係してるの？
msgctxt "0105"
msgid ""
"There would have to be some kind of <CLT 3>hidden\n"
"connection<CLT> there, don't you think?"
msgstr ""

#. ボクが教えられるのは１つだけだよ…
msgctxt "0106"
msgid "Some deeper truth...that we just don't understand..."
msgstr ""

#. すべての答えは、
#. オマエラの<CLT 03>『奪われた学園生活の記憶』<CLT>にある！
msgctxt "0107"
msgid "Can't be! It's a fake!"
msgstr ""

#. じゃあ返せ！　その記憶をオレらに返せよ！
msgctxt "0108"
msgid ""
"But Monokuma said it was real. I know we could just\n"
"write that off as a lie, but..."
msgstr ""

#. いやいや、記憶を奪ったのは未来機関だから、
#. "今のボク"にはどうしようもないんだよね。
msgctxt "0109"
msgid ""
"Then you trust Monokuma's word over the people who\n"
"have died?"
msgstr ""

#. なんにしても許せないね…！
msgctxt "0110"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

#. 希望を踏みにじろうとする輩なんて許せない…
#. 滅びればいいんだよ…！
msgctxt "0111"
msgid "That's what you're saying, isn't it?"
msgstr ""

#. だー！　また訳わかんねー事になってきやがった！
#. メンドクセーなァ！！
msgctxt "0112"
msgid "No, that's not it..."
msgstr ""

#. いいから、もう家に帰らせてくれ！
#. 船の部品ってのはどこにあんだよッ！？
msgctxt "0113"
msgid ""
"I'm shocked. You told everyone how we should believe\n"
"in our friends, but you refuse to do the same."
msgstr ""

#. さぁ、どこでしょうね？
#. この島のどこかにあるはずなんだけどね。
msgctxt "0114"
msgid "Th-That's not—!"
msgstr ""

#. この島はもう一通り見て回りましたが…
#. 船の部品なんてどこにもありませんでしたよ？
msgctxt "0115"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>What's going on, Kyoko? Why are you getting so\n"
"emotional...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. いや…まだドッキリハウスが残ってたはずだ。
msgctxt "0116"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I don't understand why she's so angry...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 聞く話によれば…メンバー全員が揃わぬ限り、
#. 辿り着けない場所であったな？
msgctxt "0117"
msgid ""
"C'mon guys, stop fighting, or all your good luck is\n"
"gonna float away!"
msgstr ""

#. ピンポーン！　大正解！
msgctxt "0118"
msgid ""
"Anyway, Makoto...you're thinking about it too much.\n"
"There's no way Monokuma didn't fake that picture."
msgstr ""

#. そう、まだ見つかってないご褒美は、
#. すべてドッキリハウスの中に隠してありまーす！
msgctxt "0119"
msgid ""
"He's just trying to confuse us. You shouldn't listen\n"
"to anything Monokuma has to say."
msgstr ""

#. そこに、船の部品もあんだなッ！？
msgctxt "0120"
msgid "Y-You might be right, but still..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>いや、船の部品だけじゃない…
#. すべてのご褒美って事は…<CLT>
msgctxt "0121"
msgid "Are you still so conflicted?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>俺達の希望ヶ峰学園時代のプロフィール…もだ。<CLT>
msgctxt "0122"
msgid "It looks like you guys have stopped playing nice."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>つまり、"俺の才能"の手掛かりも、
#. そこにあるって事だ。<CLT>
msgctxt "0123"
msgid "Byakuya!"
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0124"
msgid "You all have the same sunken look on your faces."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>罠かもしれない…
#. 罠かもしれないけど…<CLT>
msgctxt "0125"
msgid ""
"You were all so ugly before. You shouldn't let them\n"
"sink any lower."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>だけど…<CLT>
msgctxt "0126"
msgid ""
"When I look at you, it makes me think of a frog\n"
"sinking into a pile of manure."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>どうせ、とっくに罠にかかっているんだ。
#. だったら…<CLT>
msgctxt "0127"
msgid "Sorry..."
msgstr ""

#. みんな…行こう…
msgctxt "0128"
msgid "Why are you apologizing!?"
msgstr ""

#. ドッキリハウスに行ってみよう…！
msgctxt "0129"
msgid "Leave us alone! You're not a part of this!"
msgstr ""

#. ですが…大丈夫なのでしょうか？
#. ドッキリハウスってあの不気味な建物ですよね？
msgctxt "0130"
msgid ""
"That's true enough. Your problems aren't mine. We are,\n"
"and always will be, completely separate."
msgstr ""

#. でも…行くしかないだろ。
msgctxt "0131"
msgid ""
"So whatever's causing your faces to turn so ugly has\n"
"absolutely nothing to do with me."
msgstr ""

#. だって、そこに行けば
#. 船の部品が手に入るかも知れないんだぞ！
msgctxt "0132"
msgid ""
"And if I happened to discover a <CLT 3>vital clue<CLT>, it\n"
"wouldn't concern you in the slightest."
msgstr ""

#. …それに、日向クンの才能の秘密もね。
msgctxt "0133"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0134"
msgid "Did he finally just say something useful?"
msgstr ""

#. いいよ…日向クンの意見を尊重して、
#. ボクらもドッキリハウスに向かうとしようか。
msgctxt "0135"
msgid "...Byakuya. What have you been up to?"
msgstr ""

#. うぷぷ、どうやら決まったみたいだね。
msgctxt "0136"
msgid ""
"I don't mind telling you. Perhaps forcing your lazy\n"
"brains to get to work might do you some good."
msgstr ""

#. じゃあ、ボクは準備があるから先に行ってよーっと！
#. また後でねー！
msgctxt "0137"
msgid ""
"I was <CLT 3>in the bath<CLT>. What else would you like to know?\n"
"Today's lottery numbers?"
msgstr ""

#. うーん、あんまり気乗りしないけど…
msgctxt "0138"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>He was...taking a bath?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. でも、みんなが行くって言うなら仕方ないか。
#. 一緒に行くしかないよね。
msgctxt "0139"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Is he saying he's been talking to <CLT><CLT 3>Alter Ego<CLT><CLT 4>? Did he\n"
"tell him something...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 自ら罠に飛び込むなど狂気の沙汰だが…
msgctxt "0140"
msgid "Maybe we should *all* go take a bath."
msgstr ""

#. フハハハッ！　だからこそ面白いッ！！
msgctxt "0141"
msgid "Ah...good idea."
msgstr ""

#. じゃあ、決まりだな…！
msgctxt "0142"
msgid "A mixed bath...?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>あの"未来機関のファイル"で、
#. 新たな謎を突き付けられたせいかもしれないけど…<CLT>
msgctxt "0143"
msgid "A mixed bath...!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>…俺は焦っていた。<CLT>
msgctxt "0144"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>If Alter Ego really did tell him something...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>次から次へと訳のわからない謎を突き付けられて、
#. じっとしていられなかったんだ。<CLT>
msgctxt "0145"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>...I wonder what it could have been.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
